    "Furthermore, LibSVM's multilanguage support and extensive documentation further enhance its recognition and adoption in the research community, solidifying its position as a valuable tool for researchers exploring CSL.",
    "KEEL (2018), an open-source Java software tool, appeared twice (1.2%) in the selected research.",
